app_name: Beat Maker Pro - DJ Drum Pad
description:
Are you looking for the ultimate beat-making trainer? Look no further and choose Beat Maker Pro.

Beat Maker Pro will boost your rhythm skills through guided beat-making lessons, whether you are a beginner or an advanced musician. If you wonder… YES, beat-making is for everyone!

Beat Maker Pro is your ideal music coach that will guide you through beat composition in no time.

Play your first song in three lessons, then improve with our skill-building exercises, challenge yourself and keep making beats!

Enjoy our regularly updated world-class catalogue, including famous tracks and sample packs made by professional beat-makers. 

Features:

- Train to play pads with over 1000 lessons and unique sound packs
- Learn tips and tricks conceived by experienced beat makers
- Master all music styles: EDM, trap, house, pop, electro…and more
- Tap and Learn: intuitive drum pads
- Creative finger drumming. Use drums, piano, and FX
- Share your music and beat productions with the world!
- Challenge yourself in our career mode and earn Superstar status!

Premium benefits:

The premium subscription allows you to access all the present and upcoming Premium features and remove all ads from your experience. It also gives you access to exclusive sample packs in our catalogue all regularly uploaded sample packs.



Privacy Policy & Terms of Service: http://musicworldmedia.com/products/drum-pad/tos

Spotify Premium – a great way to enjoy the benefits of an offline music player and stream music without Wi-Fi. By pressing download, you can access your songs, playlists, podcasts and audiobooks offline, wherever you are.
• Listen to music, podcasts and audiobooks – all in one place
• Ad-free music listening: enjoy your music with no ad interruptions

• Audiobooks in Premium are currently available in the UK, US, Australia, Ireland, New Zealand and Canada. Discover 250,000+ audiobook titles with 15 hours/month of available listening for Premium Individual subscribers and Duo & Family plan managers.

Spotify lets you play music wherever you are. Listen to your favourite songs and discover new music, podcasts and audiobooks with the Spotify app!

Amplify your imagination. Powered by the world’s most advanced AI music model, Suno transforms your ideas into songs—no instruments needed, just your creative vision. Whether you’re a shower-singer, aspiring songwriter, or charting artist, Suno empowers you to create and discover music like never before.

Generate music from prompts, images, or videos with the world’s best AI music model:
• Transform your ideas into fully-produced songs and beats with a single prompt. Create 10 songs or beats per day at no cost.
• Inspiration begins with you. Write a text prompt like "Create a rap song about walking my dog," sing a melody, hum a tune, or tap out a beat.
• Record or upload audio to personalize your music, or generate songs from images and videos.

Write original lyrics with effortlessly:
• Whether you're in your feels with emotional ballads, hyped on energetic rap verses, or hooked on catchy pop, our lyrics generator and AI songwriter helps you craft custom lyrics that match your style and creative vision.

Create playlists for every mood and moment:
• Curate your personal AI music library and organize your favorite tracks, beats, and instrumentals into playlists you can revisit anytime.
• Manage your AI songs, view track details, and fine-tune your playlists—your music making journey is uniquely yours with Suno.

Discover new music and connect with artists:
• Stay inspired by listening to tracks created by other users and explore the best AI music across genres like rock, rap, hip hop, pop, and more.
• Find fresh favorites by browsing trending music and follow artists to stay connected.
• Discover new voice styles, AI covers, rising talent, and beat makers from around the world.

Music has no boundaries at Suno. Anything you imagine can take shape as a song to share. Whether you're taking your first steps in music making or chasing your next hit, infinite possibilities begin with a simple prompt in our AI song generator. Feeling pro? Take full creative control: adjust vocals, tweak structure, fine-tune melodies, and edit every detail to your vision.

Suno is how imagination becomes music, and music becomes yours.

The official app for setting up and controlling your Sonos products. 

Sonos is the premium wireless sound system that makes it simple to fill your home with brilliant sound for music, home cinema, and more. Customise your system with speakers, soundbars, and components that connect over WiFi. Stream any song, podcast, audiobook, or radio station to any room, and elevate your TV, movie, and gaming experiences. 

Easily set up your system. 
Get step-by-step instructions for setting up and adding speakers.

Control your system from any room. 
With the Sonos app, you can control all your speakers, soundbars, and components. Adjust volume levels, group products to play in sync, or play something different in every room. 

Connect your favourite services. 
Sonos is more than an app. It’s a smart platform that brings together hundreds of services for streaming and control, including voice control. Browse all your music, podcasts, radio, and audiobooks in one place. 

Enjoy exclusive access to Sonos Radio. 
Listen to thousands of stations free on your system, including live radio from round the world, genre stations, artist-curated stations, and original programming from Sonos. 

Enhance your home cinema experience. 
Sonos soundbars feature special settings for TV, movies, and gaming. Turn on Speech Enhancement to emphasise the frequencies associated with the human voice and clarify dialogue, or enable Night Sound to reduce loud sound effects when you don’t want to disturb others in the house. 

Custom-tune your speakers. 
Trueplay™ puts the speaker-tuning capability of the pros in the palm of your hands, customising the sound of the speaker to the unique acoustics of the room.

Personalise your settings. 
Save favourites to My Sonos to get to the music faster, create alarms so you can wake up to a favourite radio station or playlist, filter explicit content, and more.

What's that song? Shazam will instantly identify music playing around you or in apps like TikTok, Instagram, YouTube & Snapchat. Discover concerts near you, song lyrics, videos & more. With tens of millions of daily users, Shazam is trusted by music lovers worldwide.

“Shazam is a gift... a game changer” – Pharrell Williams, GQ 
“I don't know how we ever survived before Shazam” – Marshmello 
“Shazam is a kind of magic… You hear a song, hold your phone up like a wand and it tells you exactly what song it is, who sang it and lets you add it to your playlist or share it to your social media… How is that not magic?!” – Calum Scott

WHY YOU’LL LOVE IT

* Identify music in an instant.
* Discover live shows near you from your favourite artists or through curated recommendations.
* Recognise songs even when you’re offline, using headphones or on a different app.
* Revisit your music discovery history in your library anytime.
* Get recommended songs and playlists similar to the music you’ve discovered.

USE SHAZAM ANYWHERE, ANYTIME

* Enable the Shazam widgets on your Lock Screen or Home Screen.
* Ask Siri, “What’s this song?” to use Shazam hands-free.
* Automate music discovery with the Shazam Shortcut in the Shortcuts app.

CONNECT WITH YOUR MUSIC

* Unlock extras from artists around the world.
* Open any song directly in Apple Music, Spotify, YouTube Music, Amazon Music & Deezer.
* Listen and add songs directly to your Apple Music playlists.
* Watch music videos of the songs you discover in Apple Music or YouTube.
* Follow along to songs with real-time, karaoke-style lyrics.
* See what’s trending locally and globally with Shazam Charts.

Availability and features may vary by country. For more information on Shazam’s privacy practices, please read the Privacy Policy, available at https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/. Find out more and get support from AppleCare at https://support.apple.com/guide/shazam/welcome.

SIGNATURE EXPERIENCE
Enjoy our signature design as you turn your smartphone into a Bang & Olufsen-designed control centre. The app showcases the striking Bang & Olufsen products connected to your Bang & Olufsen account.

SETUP GUIDANCE & PERSONALIZATION
The Bang & Olufsen app guides you step-by-step through the setup of your product and helps you personalize your product and music experience.

BANG & OLUFSEN SIGNATURE SOUND
Easy access to product-specific sound settings of your Bang & Olufsen product, giving you beautiful sound no matter what you are listening to. 

LATEST UPDATE
Never miss an update. The Bang & Olufsen app will notify you about updates for your products.

INSTRUCTIONS AND USER GUIDE
The Bang & Olufsen app guides you on how to use your product and how to get the most out of the product-specific features. We also ensure you easy access to your product’s user guide.

NOTE
Bang & Olufsen app replaces BeoSetup app for product set-up, BeoRemote app for operating your Bang & Olufsen TV, and BeoPlay app for setting up and controlling your BeoPlay product.

Sound Profiles 
Pick between different sound profiles to find the right sound for your vibe.  

Custom EQ 
Want more bass? Need to tweak the treble. The power is at your fingertip.  

TeamUp & SKAA Pro Mode 
Link up to five Soundboks to create DIY soundsystems and unlimited Lightboks* for immersive atmospheres. You can rely on SKAA Pro's audio quality and latency to come in clutch.  

ProPanel & Performance Modes 
Does your mic need more volume? Mixer sounding thin? Use the ProPanel's performance modes to fine-tune your inputs.  

Energy Levels & Color Palettes 
Choose between three energy levels and 10 curated color palettes for ultimate atmosphere control.  

PIN-code 
Register your Soundboks and set your pin to protect your speaker from gate crashers.  

Firmware Upgrades 
Get firmware upgrades direct to your app and keep your Soundboks sounding tip top.  

In-App Feedback Form 
Something playing up? Take a screenshot to trigger the feedback form and tell us how we can help.

Things have moved on. There’s no longer just a dial to twist when your favourite song comes on, then guard to make sure no one else touches it. With the app, you can crank up the volume from the kitchen and there’s nothing anyone can do about it. 

It’s using the powers of technology for good, and ultimately with you in control, better playlists for all. And if apps aren’t your thing, you can still use our products without it. 

Using the app is simple. Just connect your devices, adjust the volume, and get on with your life. You can fiddle with more detailed adjustments if you’re that way inclined, like equalisers and noise control for headphones – everything is there to help create your perfect fit.

Access the world's largest catalogue of guitar, bass & ukulele chords, tabs, and lyrics. Challenge yourself to learn your favourite songs and more!
 
You have choices galore:
 
• Search for songs by genre, rating, your ability, tuning level
• Explore UG Tab collections. Use the finder for your faves, fall in love with something new, feel the nostalgic vibes. Search by themes like House or Acoustic, or check out the latest album releases. Find collections based on your interests such as Star Wars or funky Bollywood beats.
• Focus on guitar techniques, find songs personal to you in collections from professional guitarists
• Anytime you feel inspired to share a song, create and upload your shot on the spot. It’s that easy! Share the best parts of your performance with your like minded community of fellow musicians.
• Reach your true musical potential – learn to play with UG Courses here. Access over 2500 lessons for any skill level and instrument type from guitar, drums to piano and more. Learn different styles and techniques with guidance from professional musicians. Progress at your own speed and on any device, anytime, anywhere.
• Play over 26,000 popular songs in their original sound with Tonebridge Guitar Effects
 
And it doesn’t end there
 
Check out all these features:
• More than 1,000,000 songs to explore guitar, bass & ukulele chords, tabs, and lyrics
• Watch videos of songs to refresh your memory or use as backing tracks
• Compile your favourite tabs in playlists from our tab collections

• Set a font style and size to match the tab
• Offline access to favourite tabs - available at all times
• Enjoy dark mode for a gig
 
With a Pro account:
• Use interactive tabs to play songs note by note, at your own pace
• Select the chord variation that best suits you from the world's biggest library of chords
• Use ‘Simplify’  to make difficult songs easier
• Jam with high quality tabs - over 22,500 that include backing tracks and synchronised lyrics

• Transpose songs to get just the right tone for you
• Take advantage of autoscroll during your practice sessions
• Achieve the right sound with the built-in guitar tuner
• Share, print, and export your fave songs
 
Problems or feedback?
We are always eager to improve your Tabs experience and strive for excellence in doing so. Let us help you in person by contacting our development team at support.ios@ultimate-guitar.com, and we will endeavour to meet your needs.
Please do not post bug reports or feature requests as an App Store review.
